579
00:28:29,380 --> 00:28:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] koje smo podizali u svojim životima

580
00:28:31,579 --> 00:28:34,180
[SPEAKER_00] i kako zapravo dolazi

581
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:36,180
[SPEAKER_00] do ozdravljenja

582
00:28:36,180 --> 00:28:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] uslijed odrastanja i ona dva procesa

583
00:28:39,380 --> 00:28:40,299
[SPEAKER_00] o kojem smo pričali,

584
00:28:40,299 --> 00:28:42,319
[SPEAKER_00] koje se događa u svakom čovjeku,

585
00:28:42,319 --> 00:28:47,420
[SPEAKER_00] to se događa samo u zdravom okruženju,

586
00:28:47,420 --> 00:28:48,839
[SPEAKER_00] u zajedništvu.

587
00:28:48,839 --> 00:28:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] Rekla bi čak u crkvenom zajedništvu.

588
00:28:52,859 --> 00:28:55,220
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ja ću vam ispričat svoju priču

589
00:28:55,220 --> 00:28:56,140
[SPEAKER_00] što se dogodilo

590
00:28:56,140 --> 00:28:58,680
[SPEAKER_00] kod mene u životu.

591
00:28:58,680 --> 00:29:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da razvesnimo na početku,

592
00:29:02,519 --> 00:29:05,799
[SPEAKER_00] ovo nije jedno svjedočanstvo

593
00:29:05,799 --> 00:29:07,059
[SPEAKER_00] o nepoznavanju Boga

594
00:29:07,059 --> 00:29:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] pa o nadnaravnoj objavi promjeni srca

595
00:29:10,500 --> 00:29:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] ili o mnoštvu grijeha

596
00:29:12,599 --> 00:29:13,619
[SPEAKER_00] pa jednoj ispovjedi

597
00:29:13,619 --> 00:29:15,200
[SPEAKER_00] gdje se sve okrenulo.

598
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo također nije svjedočanstvo

599
00:29:18,480 --> 00:29:21,859
[SPEAKER_00] o jednoj jedinoj

600
00:29:21,859 --> 00:29:24,240
[SPEAKER_00] Božjoj intervenciji

601
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:26,099
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam, u mom životu

602
00:29:26,099 --> 00:29:28,160
[SPEAKER_00] nego ovako nešto

603
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:30,319
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo obično, bez senzacija.

604
00:29:30,319 --> 00:29:33,299
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo svi Goran Čurković

605
00:29:33,299 --> 00:29:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] i Simona Gotovac

606
00:29:34,559 --> 00:29:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] i uvijek nam je drago čuti

607
00:29:37,119 --> 00:29:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] takve nevjerojatne priče.

608
00:29:38,500 --> 00:29:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno, em nam dižu vjeru,

609
00:29:40,559 --> 00:29:42,200
[SPEAKER_00] em nas ostavljaju bez teksta,

610
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] pokazuju nam Božju veličinu,

611
00:29:45,099 --> 00:29:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] ali ipak nas je statistički

612
00:29:47,579 --> 00:29:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] više ovako običnih, jel tako?

613
00:29:50,859 --> 00:29:53,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, zato ću vam ja danas posvjedočiti.

614
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, kome ne zna, ja sam dragica,

615
00:29:58,500 --> 00:29:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] imam 25 godina

616
00:29:59,920 --> 00:30:03,319
[SPEAKER_00] i ako me zna, znači je dobro

617
00:30:03,319 --> 00:30:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] da kod mene u životu ništa nije išlo

618
00:30:05,319 --> 00:30:07,059
[SPEAKER_00] lako i jednostavno,

619
00:30:07,059 --> 00:30:09,200
[SPEAKER_00] nego često turbulentno i dinamično.

620
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:13,339
[SPEAKER_00] I teško mi je nekako pronać neke momente preokreta

621
00:30:13,339 --> 00:30:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] u mom životu, kao što sam rekla,

622
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] iako sigurno je bilo.

623
00:30:17,380 --> 00:30:19,839
[SPEAKER_00] Nego, ja sam jedna sasvim obična,

624
00:30:19,839 --> 00:30:21,619
[SPEAKER_00] klasična djevojka koja je

625
00:30:21,619 --> 00:30:23,339
[SPEAKER_00] od početka svog života

626
00:30:23,339 --> 00:30:24,839
[SPEAKER_00] vođena na svetu misu.

627
00:30:24,839 --> 00:30:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] Od malena sam aktivna i u župi,

628
00:30:27,980 --> 00:30:28,900
[SPEAKER_00] znači župljani,

629
00:30:29,380 --> 00:30:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] kroz razne igrokaze, recitacije,

630
00:30:31,599 --> 00:30:33,779
[SPEAKER_00] predstave razne i tako dalje.

631
00:30:33,779 --> 00:30:37,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kasnije onda je li čitanje na sveti misama,

632
00:30:37,019 --> 00:30:38,180
[SPEAKER_00] pjevanje u zboru.

633
00:30:38,180 --> 00:30:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] A evo, stvarno, kroz cijeli život.

634
00:30:40,380 --> 00:30:43,759
[SPEAKER_00] U trenutku polaska mladih na zajednicu

635
00:30:43,759 --> 00:30:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] kod Matije Ricova,

636
00:30:44,880 --> 00:30:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam na poziv njegove tadašnje žene,

637
00:30:48,539 --> 00:30:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] a moje dugogodišnje prijateljice i kume Danijele,

638
00:30:51,599 --> 00:30:54,099
[SPEAKER_00] došla na susret i mogu reći da sam bila,

639
00:30:54,099 --> 00:30:55,400
[SPEAKER_00] znači, među prvim mladima,

640
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] kao što je Mišo već rekao.

641
00:30:58,059 --> 00:31:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam otad članica na novorođeni,

642
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:03,140
[SPEAKER_00] kuhana i pečena, što bi se reklo,

643
00:31:03,140 --> 00:31:03,740
[SPEAKER_00] od 2014.

644
00:31:03,740 --> 00:31:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, skoro deset godina.

645
00:31:06,420 --> 00:31:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] I sad pitali bi me gorljivi dečki

646
00:31:10,940 --> 00:31:11,900
[SPEAKER_00] iz Novog travnika,

647
00:31:11,900 --> 00:31:14,200
[SPEAKER_00] ih, jel sad proroštvo idu ko luda?

648
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem, nažalost, ne.

649
00:31:17,599 --> 00:31:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možda u tolikoj mjeri,

650
00:31:19,519 --> 00:31:21,519
[SPEAKER_00] koliko bi po nekoj matematici godina

651
00:31:21,519 --> 00:31:22,660
[SPEAKER_00] trebalo biti,

652
00:31:22,660 --> 00:31:26,160
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije do Boga, nego do mene.

653
00:31:26,740 --> 00:31:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] U čemu je stvar?

654
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:31,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bih danas cijela progovoriti

655
00:31:31,220 --> 00:31:34,400
[SPEAKER_00] o lažima u koje sam povjerovala

656
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:35,700
[SPEAKER_00] i saživila se s njima

657
00:31:35,700 --> 00:31:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] tokom svog života,

658
00:31:37,420 --> 00:31:39,640
[SPEAKER_00] ovog zemaljskoga i naravno duhovnog,

659
00:31:39,640 --> 00:31:42,119
[SPEAKER_00] jer, pazite, imala sam 16 godina

660
00:31:42,119 --> 00:31:42,779
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam došla,

661
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:46,900
[SPEAKER_00] teško mi je odvojiti to neko sazrijevanje put rasta,

662
00:31:46,900 --> 00:31:48,200
[SPEAKER_00] boli od rastanja,

663
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:50,039
[SPEAKER_00] od sazrijevanja i puta u zajednici.

664
00:31:50,039 --> 00:31:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] Pa,

665
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] prva laž

666
00:31:54,039 --> 00:31:55,880
[SPEAKER_00] u koju sam povjerovala

667
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:58,359
[SPEAKER_00] je da mi je

668
00:31:58,359 --> 00:31:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bog Otac dalek

669
00:31:59,539 --> 00:32:02,359
[SPEAKER_00] i da mi može biti blizu

670
00:32:02,359 --> 00:32:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] samo onolko koliko se ja njemu budem

671
00:32:04,420 --> 00:32:05,299
[SPEAKER_00] približavala

672
00:32:05,299 --> 00:32:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] kroz molitvene

673
00:32:06,980 --> 00:32:09,819
[SPEAKER_00] pobožnosti, disciplinu i tako.

674
00:32:09,819 --> 00:32:12,819
[SPEAKER_00] Druga laž je

675
00:32:12,819 --> 00:32:14,859
[SPEAKER_00] da ja moram zaslužiti njegovu ljubav

676
00:32:14,859 --> 00:32:17,220
[SPEAKER_00] zalaganjem također u molitvi

677
00:32:17,220 --> 00:32:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] post uklanjanju pobožnostima.

678
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:20,759
[SPEAKER_00] I treća laž

679
00:32:20,759 --> 00:32:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] je da je

680
00:32:22,039 --> 00:32:24,279
[SPEAKER_00] moj neuspješan život

681
00:32:24,279 --> 00:32:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] rezultat

682
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:27,339
[SPEAKER_00] moje neblizine s Bogom.

683
00:32:27,339 --> 00:32:29,160
[SPEAKER_00] Odnosno da je to zapravo

684
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:31,140
[SPEAKER_00] njegova neka kazna meni

685
00:32:31,140 --> 00:32:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] za nedovoljno zalaganje.

686
00:32:32,539 --> 00:32:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] I evo te tri laži

687
00:32:36,019 --> 00:32:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] su me zapravo sprečavale

688
00:32:38,039 --> 00:32:38,700
[SPEAKER_00] da ostvarim

689
00:32:38,700 --> 00:32:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] osoban odnos s Bogom

690
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] sam u sebe

691
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] da postanem svoj čovjek

692
00:32:45,019 --> 00:32:47,700
[SPEAKER_00] a na kraju i da služim u zajednici.

693
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:52,400
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, zašto sam povjerovala u ove laži?

694
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kod nas ljudi to naravno biva

695
00:32:56,079 --> 00:32:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] kad nekako projiciramo

696
00:32:57,980 --> 00:33:00,200
[SPEAKER_00] roditelje sa Bogom

697
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:02,819
[SPEAKER_00] i to je nekako neizbježno.

698
00:33:02,819 --> 00:33:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] Moj tata je radio,

699
00:33:05,380 --> 00:33:07,440
[SPEAKER_00] čovjek nije imao previše vremena,

700
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] nismo sad tu imali nekog vremena

701
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] za previše razgovora,

702
00:33:11,819 --> 00:33:13,319
[SPEAKER_00] druženja i tako dalje.

703
00:33:13,319 --> 00:33:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] Rekla bi jedna moja prijateljica

704
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] bude ti drago kad ideš na neku kontrolu

705
00:33:18,039 --> 00:33:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] ili upisat se u srednju

706
00:33:19,960 --> 00:33:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] pa ta dva, tri sata moraš provesti s tatom.

707
00:33:22,380 --> 00:33:24,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, malo ti je stres

708
00:33:24,039 --> 00:33:25,519
[SPEAKER_00] kao šta će te pričat,

709
00:33:25,519 --> 00:33:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] šta će te pitat,

710
00:33:26,960 --> 00:33:29,539
[SPEAKER_00] ali opet i na kraju bude drago.

711
00:33:29,539 --> 00:33:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] i nekako te trenutke

712
00:33:31,539 --> 00:33:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] smatraš i dragocijenim

713
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:34,579
[SPEAKER_00] i uvijek ih se rado sjećaš.

714
00:33:35,220 --> 00:33:37,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo, upravo, ta laž,

715
00:33:37,319 --> 00:33:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] da mi je otac dalek i da ovisi o meni koliko ću se ja njemu približavati,

716
00:33:41,539 --> 00:33:47,140
[SPEAKER_00] ona i to moje zamjeranje roditeljima

717
00:33:47,140 --> 00:33:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] i odbijanje, ajmo reći, oprosta,

718
00:33:51,019 --> 00:33:54,079
[SPEAKER_00] me vodilo u uspoređivanje s drugima,

719
00:33:54,079 --> 00:33:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] njihove startne pozicije su bolje nego moje.

720
00:33:58,980 --> 00:34:00,579
[SPEAKER_00] Također, druga laž,

721
00:34:00,579 --> 00:34:02,299
[SPEAKER_00] da moram zaslužiti,

722
00:34:02,299 --> 00:34:03,240
[SPEAKER_00] koliko dajem,

723
00:34:03,240 --> 00:34:04,359
[SPEAKER_00] toliko mi se i vraća,

724
00:34:04,359 --> 00:34:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] tu isto normalno budeš uvjeren

725
00:34:06,539 --> 00:34:07,900
[SPEAKER_00] zbog nekih, eto, donošenja,

726
00:34:07,900 --> 00:34:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] petica, kući, čišćenja,

727
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno ne, čišćenja, kuće

728
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:13,400
[SPEAKER_00] i jednostavno,

729
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] to isto vjerujem

730
00:34:14,559 --> 00:34:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] da se svi možete pronaći u tome.

731
00:34:18,400 --> 00:34:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja opet,

732
00:34:19,519 --> 00:34:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] iako sam znala to sve razumski,

733
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:23,880
[SPEAKER_00] opet odbijam se suočit

734
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:26,400
[SPEAKER_00] s tim lažima u mom životu,

735
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] uprostit roditeljima za početak

736
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] i ostvarit osoban odnos z Bogom.

737
00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:35,019
[SPEAKER_00] S druge strane,

738
00:34:35,019 --> 00:34:36,280
[SPEAKER_00] još jedan razlog,

739
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:38,860
[SPEAKER_00] vidim oko sebe ljude u zajednici

740
00:34:38,860 --> 00:34:42,739
[SPEAKER_00] koji svojim zalaganjem postižu službe,

741
00:34:42,739 --> 00:34:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] zna se za njih,

742
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:46,019
[SPEAKER_00] došli su vremenski i za mene,

743
00:34:46,019 --> 00:34:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] a rastu kogljive u duhovnosti,

744
00:34:48,400 --> 00:34:49,780
[SPEAKER_00] i jednostavno ono,

745
00:34:49,780 --> 00:34:52,719
[SPEAKER_00] baš su gonjeni oduševljenjem za Bogom,

746
00:34:52,719 --> 00:34:54,280
[SPEAKER_00] disciplinirani,

747
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:56,280
[SPEAKER_00] ja tu preuzimam laž

748
00:34:56,280 --> 00:34:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] da i ja tako moram sve zaslužiti,

749
00:34:58,619 --> 00:34:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] jer koliko dajem,

750
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] toliko mi se i vraća.

751
00:35:01,119 --> 00:35:04,099
[SPEAKER_00] Upadam u jedno negativno uspoređivanje,

752
00:35:04,099 --> 00:35:05,760
[SPEAKER_00] umjesto da na ljude,

753
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:08,599
[SPEAKER_00] te ljude gledam kao svoje zdrave uzore.

754
00:35:08,599 --> 00:35:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] Treća laž,

755
00:35:12,980 --> 00:35:15,159
[SPEAKER_00] neuspješan život

756
00:35:15,159 --> 00:35:18,320
[SPEAKER_00] kao kazna za nedovoljno zalaganje,

757
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:19,860
[SPEAKER_00] ista stvar,

758
00:35:19,860 --> 00:35:22,780
[SPEAKER_00] u životu moraš sve sam zaslužiti,

759
00:35:22,780 --> 00:35:24,019
[SPEAKER_00] zaraditi,

760
00:35:24,019 --> 00:35:24,719
[SPEAKER_00] snaći se,

761
00:35:24,719 --> 00:35:26,780
[SPEAKER_00] da bi nešto postigao,

762
00:35:26,780 --> 00:35:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] ako nisi radio, nisi zaradio,

763
00:35:29,179 --> 00:35:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] ako nisi uštedio, nisi štedio,

764
00:35:31,039 --> 00:35:32,780
[SPEAKER_00] ako nisi učio, nisi naučio.

765
00:35:32,780 --> 00:35:34,280
[SPEAKER_00] I evo,

766
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] hvala Bogu,

767
00:35:36,380 --> 00:35:37,679
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno i na takvom odgoju

768
00:35:37,679 --> 00:35:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] mogu vidjeti jako dobre plodove,

769
00:35:39,380 --> 00:35:41,820
[SPEAKER_00] što se tiče financija i odgovornosti

770
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:42,760
[SPEAKER_00] u svom životu,

771
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali

772
00:35:43,619 --> 00:35:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] tek s odmakom.

773
00:35:45,480 --> 00:35:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

774
00:35:46,119 --> 00:35:47,239
[SPEAKER_00] u tim trenucima,

775
00:35:47,239 --> 00:35:48,219
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam ja

776
00:35:48,219 --> 00:35:49,820
[SPEAKER_00] tu laž,

777
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:50,980
[SPEAKER_00] kad je ta laž bila

778
00:35:50,980 --> 00:35:53,179
[SPEAKER_00] u mom životu utvrda,

779
00:35:53,179 --> 00:35:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] ja preuzimam identite žrtve,

780
00:35:55,820 --> 00:35:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] moram nešto što drugi ne moraju,

781
00:35:58,440 --> 00:36:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] moram previše raditi,

782
00:36:00,079 --> 00:36:00,780
[SPEAKER_00] tako dalje.

783
00:36:00,780 --> 00:36:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] I s druge strane,

784
00:36:04,039 --> 00:36:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] u zajednici vidim da

785
00:36:05,980 --> 00:36:08,599
[SPEAKER_00] uspješan život vode osobe

786
00:36:08,599 --> 00:36:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] koji su blizu Bogu,

787
00:36:10,940 --> 00:36:12,400
[SPEAKER_00] koji se trude.

788
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] Oni iz prve pronalaze muževe i žene,

789
00:36:15,039 --> 00:36:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] njima ide iz prve na fakultetu,

790
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:19,780
[SPEAKER_00] oni odmah znaju zašto su stvoreni,

791
00:36:19,780 --> 00:36:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] znaju koje su njihove službe,

792
00:36:21,460 --> 00:36:23,400
[SPEAKER_00] talenti, gdje trebaju služiti

793
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] i sve to ja smatram da je rezultat

794
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] njihove discipline.

795
00:36:29,300 --> 00:36:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] A znamo da objektivno nije tako,

796
00:36:31,039 --> 00:36:33,119
[SPEAKER_00] jer stvarno je mali broj

797
00:36:33,119 --> 00:36:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] van serijskih igrača,

798
00:36:34,619 --> 00:36:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam, u našoj zajednici,

799
00:36:36,039 --> 00:36:37,679
[SPEAKER_00] kojima je stvarno sve išlo iz prve,

800
00:36:37,679 --> 00:36:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] nego jednostavno to je jedna naša

801
00:36:39,900 --> 00:36:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] kriva percepcija.

802
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako je Bog otirao laži

803
00:36:44,340 --> 00:36:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] iz mog života

804
00:36:45,920 --> 00:36:48,219
[SPEAKER_00] i kako sam povjerovala u njegovu ljubav?

805
00:36:48,219 --> 00:36:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što sam rekla,

806
00:36:50,659 --> 00:36:52,639
[SPEAKER_00] meni to sve je bilo lako prihvatiti

807
00:36:52,639 --> 00:36:55,760
[SPEAKER_00] razumski, ideš i slušaš o Unboundu,

808
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] poslušala sam sto predavanja

809
00:36:57,980 --> 00:37:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] u ovih devet godina svjedočanstava svega,

810
00:37:00,500 --> 00:37:03,519
[SPEAKER_00] otkrivaš prvu božansku osobu

811
00:37:03,519 --> 00:37:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] i sve se opet svodi na to

812
00:37:05,380 --> 00:37:07,639
[SPEAKER_00] da moraš imati osoban odnos s Bogom.

813
00:37:07,639 --> 00:37:10,719
[SPEAKER_00] To je meni nekad izazivalo u meni

814
00:37:10,719 --> 00:37:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo onako jednu gorčinu,

815
00:37:13,960 --> 00:37:16,280
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam to smatrala za sebe nedostižno.

816
00:37:16,760 --> 00:37:18,179
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ja mogu upoznat oca?

817
00:37:18,179 --> 00:37:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] I baš me to provociralo.

818
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:23,719
[SPEAKER_00] Kako kod mene, očito, nije moglo iz prve.

819
00:37:23,719 --> 00:37:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam baš doživljavala neke neuspjehe

820
00:37:26,460 --> 00:37:28,360
[SPEAKER_00] na bitnim područjima života.

821
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:30,320
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna veza, druga veza,

822
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] nije završilo brakom.

823
00:37:31,559 --> 00:37:32,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan fakultet upišem,

824
00:37:32,900 --> 00:37:35,739
[SPEAKER_00] ne ide, ostavim to, upišem drugi.

825
00:37:35,739 --> 00:37:38,460
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna služba izbace me iz te službe.

826
00:37:38,619 --> 00:37:39,360
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo i toga.

827
00:37:39,360 --> 00:37:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] A za sve sam ja to i molila

828
00:37:41,980 --> 00:37:44,719
[SPEAKER_00] i bilo mi je dobro tad kada je to trajalo.

829
00:37:44,719 --> 00:37:45,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu reći stvarno.

830
00:37:45,940 --> 00:37:51,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, očito, su ti moji neuspješni pokušaji

831
00:37:51,679 --> 00:37:54,219
[SPEAKER_00] bili moji, a ne Božji.

832
00:37:54,219 --> 00:37:57,719
[SPEAKER_00] I zapravo razni ti padovi

833
00:37:57,719 --> 00:38:00,300
[SPEAKER_00] u osobnom odnosu s Bogom,

834
00:38:00,300 --> 00:38:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] to je u blizini s njim,

835
00:38:01,619 --> 00:38:03,719
[SPEAKER_00] svaki put su me vodili

836
00:38:03,719 --> 00:38:06,039
[SPEAKER_00] u jednu novu fazu stagnacije.

837
00:38:07,260 --> 00:38:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] u jedno novo uspoređivanje.

838
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:13,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kome zna, zna da sam u raznim fazama

839
00:38:13,019 --> 00:38:14,860
[SPEAKER_00] stagnirala u raznim periodima,

840
00:38:14,860 --> 00:38:15,840
[SPEAKER_00] kraćim i dužim.

841
00:38:15,840 --> 00:38:18,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to se nekako najviše očitovalo,

842
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:20,659
[SPEAKER_00] rekla bi, u službi

843
00:38:20,659 --> 00:38:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] i u mom oduševljenju za Bogom,

844
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:26,179
[SPEAKER_00] koje je znalo je njavat.

845
00:38:26,179 --> 00:38:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] I mogu reći da se

846
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] sve događalo pomalo.

847
00:38:32,599 --> 00:38:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] Odim na neku molitvu.

848
00:38:35,079 --> 00:38:36,639
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno preporučujem

849
00:38:36,639 --> 00:38:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] ako imate nekih problema

850
00:38:38,519 --> 00:38:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] koje niste mogli sami riješiti.

851
00:38:40,079 --> 00:38:41,219
[SPEAKER_00] Odite na molitvu.

852
00:38:41,219 --> 00:38:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] Zajednica nudi.

853
00:38:42,579 --> 00:38:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] Zajednica nudi ovaj

854
00:38:45,400 --> 00:38:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] osobnu molitvu.

855
00:38:46,980 --> 00:38:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] Unbound.

856
00:38:48,039 --> 00:38:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nastavim zrele u duhovnosti,

857
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:52,099
[SPEAKER_00] krenem opet na klanjanja,

858
00:38:52,099 --> 00:38:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] u jače pobožnosti,

859
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:55,400
[SPEAKER_00] pompeske devetnice itd.

860
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:57,280
[SPEAKER_00] i hop,

861
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:58,679
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mi podari momka,

862
00:38:58,679 --> 00:38:59,860
[SPEAKER_00] kakvog sam htjela,

863
00:38:59,860 --> 00:39:03,099
[SPEAKER_00] po nekih 95% podudaranja,

864
00:39:03,099 --> 00:39:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] po nekom popisu.

865
00:39:04,159 --> 00:39:06,920
[SPEAKER_00] I super, evo,

866
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:08,780
[SPEAKER_00] dao ti je Bog momka

867
00:39:08,780 --> 00:39:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] i nekako sve to klapa

868
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,659
[SPEAKER_00] i ta predbračna čistoća i sve,

869
00:39:12,659 --> 00:39:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja se opet uspoređujem s drugima.

870
00:39:14,539 --> 00:39:17,219
[SPEAKER_00] Čoveče, ništa konkretnije,

871
00:39:17,219 --> 00:39:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] ne igdje prstira na ruci.

872
00:39:20,260 --> 00:39:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ove već rađaju,

873
00:39:21,280 --> 00:39:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] imaju djecu,

874
00:39:22,019 --> 00:39:23,920
[SPEAKER_00] poženiše se svi poudavaše.

875
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ja opet ništa.

876
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] Mučim se s tom vezom.

877
00:39:27,420 --> 00:39:28,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ja opet nezadovoljna.

878
00:39:28,860 --> 00:39:31,400
[SPEAKER_00] Moj Mateo je bio,

879
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:32,760
[SPEAKER_00] rodio se,

880
00:39:32,760 --> 00:39:33,940
[SPEAKER_00] odrastao u Austriji

881
00:39:33,940 --> 00:39:35,820
[SPEAKER_00] i, ajmo reći,

882
00:39:35,820 --> 00:39:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] imali smo tu vezu na daljinu

883
00:39:37,360 --> 00:39:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] i opet i on se iz drugog pokušaja,

884
00:39:39,900 --> 00:39:40,420
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći,

885
00:39:40,420 --> 00:39:41,659
[SPEAKER_00] vratio u Hrvatsku.

886
00:39:41,659 --> 00:39:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kažem, evo,

887
00:39:43,780 --> 00:39:45,719
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam bila i dalje nezadovoljna.

888
00:39:45,719 --> 00:39:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali što Bog radi?

889
00:39:48,099 --> 00:39:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] Polako mi pokazuje talente

890
00:39:49,900 --> 00:39:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] koje mi je dao

891
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:55,159
[SPEAKER_00] i zajednica mi dodjeljuje službu

892
00:39:55,159 --> 00:39:57,639
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj sam ko riba u vodi,

893
00:39:57,639 --> 00:39:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] službu za doček

894
00:39:59,639 --> 00:40:01,320
[SPEAKER_00] i prihvat novih članova.

895
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:04,300
[SPEAKER_00] I tu mi Bog pokazuje moje dobre strane,

896
00:40:04,300 --> 00:40:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] moje talente,

897
00:40:05,199 --> 00:40:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] otvorenost komunikaciju

898
00:40:07,579 --> 00:40:12,400
[SPEAKER_00] i nekako me blagosljivlja za tu službu.

899
00:40:12,400 --> 00:40:14,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se tu osjećam dobro.

900
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećam već tu jednu odgovornost,

901
00:40:16,980 --> 00:40:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] dato povjerenje od zajednice

902
00:40:19,539 --> 00:40:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] i budem sretna na neki period,

903
00:40:22,039 --> 00:40:23,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali opet padam,

904
00:40:23,420 --> 00:40:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] stagniram,

905
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] povlačim se,

906
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:28,800
[SPEAKER_00] opet u te laži,

907
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] pa šta sam ja jedina od svog tog društva

908
00:40:31,059 --> 00:40:33,480
[SPEAKER_00] da se nisam zaručila i udala.

909
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] opet se uspoređujem,

910
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] ali kažem, ja sam stvarno molila za to,

911
00:40:39,059 --> 00:40:42,219
[SPEAKER_00] vraćala se stalno u zajedništvo,

912
00:40:42,219 --> 00:40:45,679
[SPEAKER_00] jer jednostavno ne možeš, ne možeš bježat.

913
00:40:46,039 --> 00:40:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] to se vidi kad neko bježi.

914
00:40:47,460 --> 00:40:50,280
[SPEAKER_00] Baš se moraš vraćat u to zajedništvo,

915
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:59,280
[SPEAKER_00] koje te provocira i koje ti može biti vrlo, vrlo korisno za pozitivno uspoređivanje.

916
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:03,179
[SPEAKER_00] I tako malo pomalo otac briše laži iz mog života

917
00:41:03,179 --> 00:41:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] i na meni prihvatljive načine

918
00:41:05,039 --> 00:41:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] pokazuje koliko me voli.

919
00:41:07,099 --> 00:41:07,780
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže, ajda,

920
00:41:07,780 --> 00:41:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] k'si već toko tvrdoglava,

921
00:41:09,159 --> 00:41:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] eto ti radi, muči se,

922
00:41:11,039 --> 00:41:14,639
[SPEAKER_00] kad ne znaš već širit ruke i primat,

923
00:41:14,639 --> 00:41:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

924
00:41:15,039 --> 00:41:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] šta će i on sa mnom više nije znao.

925
00:41:17,539 --> 00:41:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam stvarno radila stvarno,

926
00:41:20,500 --> 00:41:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] dok sam išla na faks,

927
00:41:21,679 --> 00:41:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] drugi znaju,

928
00:41:23,539 --> 00:41:25,300
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu na misu zbog posla,

929
00:41:25,300 --> 00:41:26,179
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu doći,

930
00:41:26,179 --> 00:41:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] moram raditi,

931
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:28,940
[SPEAKER_00] moram zaradi za svatbe,

932
00:41:28,940 --> 00:41:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] za duhovne obnove,

933
00:41:30,039 --> 00:41:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] za putovanja.

934
00:41:31,019 --> 00:41:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] I tad kreće mislijski rad zajednice uslijed korone

935
00:41:37,420 --> 00:41:39,219
[SPEAKER_00] i Matija kaže,

936
00:41:39,219 --> 00:41:42,260
[SPEAKER_00] bit ćeš moja tajnica za BIH,

937
00:41:42,260 --> 00:41:46,179
[SPEAKER_00] pomoćeš mi organizaciji putovanja,

938
00:41:46,179 --> 00:41:49,199
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi po putovanjima po BIH

939
00:41:49,199 --> 00:41:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] i to će ti biti pokriveno,

940
00:41:51,239 --> 00:41:52,420
[SPEAKER_00] financijski, jel?

941
00:41:53,539 --> 00:41:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ja čovječe, sretna,

942
00:41:54,980 --> 00:41:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] idem negdje,

943
00:41:55,960 --> 00:41:57,940
[SPEAKER_00] nisam zato dala fizički novac,

944
00:41:57,940 --> 00:41:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] nisam zaradila.

945
00:41:59,460 --> 00:42:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] I tu mi Bog pokazuje

946
00:42:01,559 --> 00:42:04,320
[SPEAKER_00] koliko sam toga propustila zapravo.

947
00:42:04,320 --> 00:42:07,679
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno nisam u Međugorje išla često,

948
00:42:07,679 --> 00:42:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] jer eto nisam imala novaca,

949
00:42:09,159 --> 00:42:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] kao jer nisam ja zaradila.

950
00:42:10,500 --> 00:42:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] I zostala sam ne samo u Međugorje,

951
00:42:13,500 --> 00:42:15,360
[SPEAKER_00] nego i razne milosti i blagoslove.

952
00:42:15,360 --> 00:42:18,519
[SPEAKER_00] I vidite,

953
00:42:18,519 --> 00:42:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek se koristimo istima latima.

954
00:42:21,940 --> 00:42:25,260
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek su tu dobrodošle i poželjne molitve,

955
00:42:25,260 --> 00:42:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] klanjanja, pobožnosti,

956
00:42:27,460 --> 00:42:29,219
[SPEAKER_00] ispovjedi, sakramenti,

957
00:42:29,219 --> 00:42:31,380
[SPEAKER_00] sveta misa, devetnice.

958
00:42:31,380 --> 00:42:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] I sve sam ja to koliko toliko,

959
00:42:35,199 --> 00:42:37,739
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne u mjeri u kojoj sam ja mislila da trebam.

960
00:42:37,739 --> 00:42:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] U mjeri kojeg sam se uspoređivala s drugima,

961
00:42:41,079 --> 00:42:42,320
[SPEAKER_00] oni su više neg ja.

962
00:42:43,320 --> 00:42:50,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ali baš Bog Otac u objavi ovoj sestri Elisabeti Eugenija Vasio,

963
00:42:50,039 --> 00:42:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] kaže da su naši grijesi poput željeza,

964
00:42:52,940 --> 00:42:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] a naša dobra dijela poput zlata.

965
00:42:55,079 --> 00:42:58,760
[SPEAKER_00] Donesemo li i tisuće kilograma željeza,

966
00:42:58,760 --> 00:43:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] ne može se usporediti sa onih par kila zlata i dobroga što mu damo.

967
00:43:03,840 --> 00:43:07,340
[SPEAKER_00] Znači vidimo koliko našeg malo truda je potrebno

968
00:43:07,340 --> 00:43:09,260
[SPEAKER_00] da Bog čini velike stvari.

969
00:43:09,260 --> 00:43:12,280
[SPEAKER_00] A kad sam ja to zapravo,

970
00:43:12,280 --> 00:43:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] kad mi Bog potpuno iskazuje svoju ljubav,

971
00:43:16,760 --> 00:43:20,239
[SPEAKER_00] tek onda kad sam ja prionula srcem u zajednicu,

972
00:43:20,239 --> 00:43:21,820
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam zavolila te ljude.

973
00:43:21,820 --> 00:43:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] I on mi u par mjeseci mijenja život doslovno.

974
00:43:26,079 --> 00:43:29,659
[SPEAKER_00] Na van, na svakom području života,

975
00:43:29,659 --> 00:43:32,239
[SPEAKER_00] na svim onim opipljivim područjima, kako?

976
00:43:33,840 --> 00:43:37,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam tu već sudjelujem u službi već, ne znam, par mjeseci

977
00:43:37,800 --> 00:43:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] i zajednica mi povjerava djevojke za duhovno praćenje,

978
00:43:40,800 --> 00:43:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] žensku formaciju i tako.

979
00:43:42,480 --> 00:43:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] Iako je to sve bilo nepoljnjivo za mene,

980
00:43:44,960 --> 00:43:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali te kad sam bila spremna primiti,

981
00:43:48,940 --> 00:43:52,139
[SPEAKER_00] pronalazi mi Bog posao,

982
00:43:52,139 --> 00:43:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] završavam fakultet,

983
00:43:54,420 --> 00:43:56,519
[SPEAKER_00] Mateo me zaručuje,

984
00:43:56,519 --> 00:43:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] postajem tetka.

985
00:43:58,619 --> 00:44:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

986
00:44:03,840 --> 00:44:12,699
[SPEAKER_00] Postajem tetka malog anđela

987
00:44:12,699 --> 00:44:14,780
[SPEAKER_00] i to sve u dva mjeseca.

988
00:44:14,780 --> 00:44:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] Znači od 28.8.

989
00:44:16,599 --> 00:44:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] do 28.10. prošle godine.

990
00:44:19,440 --> 00:44:22,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ja svakim tim događajem

991
00:44:22,900 --> 00:44:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] ono, doslovno me preplavljuju osjećaj

992
00:44:26,000 --> 00:44:27,719
[SPEAKER_00] da sam toliko voljena od oca,

993
00:44:27,719 --> 00:44:30,280
[SPEAKER_00] da bi sve on to daje.

994
00:44:30,400 --> 00:44:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] postajem mekana na Božje zahvate,

995
00:44:33,159 --> 00:44:36,780
[SPEAKER_00] napokon u životu razbija tu jednu moju tvrdoću srca,

996
00:44:36,780 --> 00:44:38,139
[SPEAKER_00] daje mi doslovno suze,

997
00:44:38,139 --> 00:44:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] pokazuje mi da mogu biti radosna,

998
00:44:41,340 --> 00:44:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] da mogu, pokazuje mi da on zapravo otac.

999
00:44:44,500 --> 00:44:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ja tu doživljavam istinsko očinstvo njegovo

1000
00:44:46,940 --> 00:44:50,280
[SPEAKER_00] i tad mogu sa svetim Augustinom reći

1001
00:44:50,280 --> 00:44:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] Bog me ljubi kao da sam njegovo jedino dijete.

1002
00:44:53,960 --> 00:44:57,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se naravno tu i dalje nastavljam truditi

1003
00:44:57,659 --> 00:44:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] i sa još većim strahopoštovanjem

1004
00:44:59,920 --> 00:45:01,900
[SPEAKER_00] i zahvalnoću za sve što mi je dao.

1005
00:45:01,900 --> 00:45:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo, znači dalje ide priča,

1006
00:45:06,579 --> 00:45:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] udala sam se, čekam bebu sad.

1007
00:45:09,159 --> 00:45:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, stvarno želim da ovo svjedočanstvo

1008
00:45:11,659 --> 00:45:14,440
[SPEAKER_00] bude jedna zahvala otcu na sve što mi je dao,

1009
00:45:14,440 --> 00:45:16,800
[SPEAKER_00] sve što je nezasluženo,

1010
00:45:16,800 --> 00:45:17,800
[SPEAKER_00] ali primljeno od njega.

1011
00:45:17,800 --> 00:45:21,780
[SPEAKER_00] I mogu reći da isceljenje,

1012
00:45:21,780 --> 00:45:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] njegovo isceljenje mog srca

1013
00:45:24,199 --> 00:45:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] je otvorilo i proširilo put prema njemu,

1014
00:45:28,000 --> 00:45:29,199
[SPEAKER_00] moj put prema njemu.

1015
00:45:29,199 --> 00:45:32,139
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, sad život postaje drugčiji,

1016
00:45:32,139 --> 00:45:33,679
[SPEAKER_00] neka nova previrjanja me čeka

1017
00:45:33,679 --> 00:45:35,820
[SPEAKER_00] i oće me se zaboraviti u službi kad rodim

1018
00:45:35,820 --> 00:45:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje, ali to su sad druge teme.

1019
00:45:40,920 --> 00:45:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ja i dalje nisam voličenje

1020
00:45:42,880 --> 00:45:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] pobožne žene koja vrti desetke krunice u ruci

1021
00:45:46,539 --> 00:45:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] ili vjerne članice na novorođeni

1022
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] koja je zapisana svaki dan,

1023
00:45:50,539 --> 00:45:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] sat vremena na klanjanju.

1024
00:45:51,940 --> 00:45:55,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ali meni je stvarno Bog pokazao

1025
00:45:55,059 --> 00:45:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] da mu treba malo mog truda

1026
00:45:57,340 --> 00:46:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] i malo moje inicijative da učini mnogo.

1027
00:46:00,519 --> 00:46:03,320
[SPEAKER_00] I naravno, sve ovo što sam rekla

1028
00:46:03,320 --> 00:46:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] i klanjanje i krunice i sve,

1029
00:46:05,000 --> 00:46:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] ja to i dalje smatram imperativom.

1030
00:46:06,980 --> 00:46:09,179
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte misliti, ograđujem se od toga

1031
00:46:09,179 --> 00:46:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] da to ne treba.

1032
00:46:10,179 --> 00:46:12,659
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, nastavljam se dalje boriti

1033
00:46:12,659 --> 00:46:13,860
[SPEAKER_00] u tim pobožnostima,

1034
00:46:13,860 --> 00:46:15,820
[SPEAKER_00] u borbi s osobnim grijesima,

1035
00:46:15,820 --> 00:46:18,639
[SPEAKER_00] raditi na osobnom odnosu s Bogom

1036
00:46:18,639 --> 00:46:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] i to me sve drži da ne padnem,

1037
00:46:20,579 --> 00:46:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ne padnem jel u oholost.

1038
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:23,519
[SPEAKER_00] I vidimo dakle,

1039
00:46:23,519 --> 00:46:25,239
[SPEAKER_00] sve ovo što smo pričali,

1040
00:46:25,239 --> 00:46:28,139
[SPEAKER_00] da se u nama odvija konstantno

1041
00:46:28,139 --> 00:46:29,420
[SPEAKER_00] ta borba između

1042
00:46:29,420 --> 00:46:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] prihvaćanja

1043
00:46:31,420 --> 00:46:33,199
[SPEAKER_00] na svoje grešnosti,

1044
00:46:33,199 --> 00:46:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] bjede,

1045
00:46:33,659 --> 00:46:34,820
[SPEAKER_00] nedostojnosti

1046
00:46:34,820 --> 00:46:36,280
[SPEAKER_00] i divljenja,

1047
00:46:36,280 --> 00:46:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] Božjeg divljenja

1048
00:46:38,380 --> 00:46:40,300
[SPEAKER_00] meni kao njegovom stvorenju.

1049
00:46:40,300 --> 00:46:42,219
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i psalm isto.

1050
00:46:42,219 --> 00:46:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] Na jednom mjestu kažu

1051
00:46:43,380 --> 00:46:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] što je čovjek da ga se spominješ,

1052
00:46:45,820 --> 00:46:46,760
[SPEAKER_00] a na drugom mjestu

1053
00:46:46,760 --> 00:46:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] David zahvalio,

1054
00:46:48,099 --> 00:46:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] hvala ti što sam stvoren tako čudesno,

1055
00:46:50,300 --> 00:46:52,179
[SPEAKER_00] što su dijela tvoja predivna.

1056
00:46:52,880 --> 00:46:53,679
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

1057
00:46:53,679 --> 00:46:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] vjerovanje,

1058
00:46:55,599 --> 00:46:57,679
[SPEAKER_00] moje vjerovanje u laži

1059
00:46:57,679 --> 00:47:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] i neoprost roditeljima,

1060
00:47:01,019 --> 00:47:02,800
[SPEAKER_00] nezdravo odvajanje od roditelja,

1061
00:47:02,800 --> 00:47:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] konstantno uspoređivanje s drugima,

1062
00:47:05,099 --> 00:47:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] je mene sprečavalo

1063
00:47:07,019 --> 00:47:08,679
[SPEAKER_00] da primam od Boga blagoslove.

1064
00:47:08,679 --> 00:47:09,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ustavim se reći,

1065
00:47:09,820 --> 00:47:10,739
[SPEAKER_00] njega je sprečavalo

1066
00:47:10,739 --> 00:47:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] da mi daje te blagoslove.

1067
00:47:12,119 --> 00:47:14,599
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo,

1068
00:47:14,599 --> 00:47:17,179
[SPEAKER_00] do kraja nećemo moći primiti

1069
00:47:17,179 --> 00:47:20,360
[SPEAKER_00] do god vjerujemo u krivog Boga,

1070
00:47:20,360 --> 00:47:22,300
[SPEAKER_00] do god imamo krivu sliku o Bogu.

1071
00:47:22,880 --> 00:47:24,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne želim da vi danas primite

1072
00:47:24,659 --> 00:47:27,360
[SPEAKER_00] jedno ohrabrenje za stagniranje

1073
00:47:27,360 --> 00:47:30,139
[SPEAKER_00] ili da primite od mene

1074
00:47:30,139 --> 00:47:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] jedan poticaj za nepokretanje

1075
00:47:33,059 --> 00:47:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] u vlastitom životu.

1076
00:47:34,159 --> 00:47:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ne želim da iz ovog izvučete poruku

1077
00:47:37,099 --> 00:47:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] ma, ako je mogla dragica tolke godine,

1078
00:47:39,619 --> 00:47:40,860
[SPEAKER_00] imam ja još vremena,

1079
00:47:40,860 --> 00:47:42,219
[SPEAKER_00] kako ćemo, lako ćemo.

1080
00:47:42,219 --> 00:47:43,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

1081
00:47:43,340 --> 00:47:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] Želim da se večeras odlučite

1082
00:47:46,059 --> 00:47:48,280
[SPEAKER_00] na rješavanje svojih problema.

1083
00:47:48,280 --> 00:47:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] Želim da večeras

1084
00:47:52,119 --> 00:47:55,679
[SPEAKER_00] gospodinu, Bogu, Otcu,

1085
00:47:55,679 --> 00:47:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] predate svoje krive slike,

1086
00:47:58,239 --> 00:47:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] svoje laži,

1087
00:47:59,900 --> 00:48:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] svoja uspoređivanja.

1088
00:48:02,119 --> 00:48:05,820
[SPEAKER_00] Jer dosta je bilo valjanja

1089
00:48:05,820 --> 00:48:07,340
[SPEAKER_00] u vlastitom blatu, je li tako?

1090
00:48:07,340 --> 00:48:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kolike milosti sam ja propustila

1091
00:48:11,199 --> 00:48:13,980
[SPEAKER_00] i kolike blagoslove u ovim godinama.

1092
00:48:13,980 --> 00:48:15,239
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto?

1093
00:48:16,239 --> 00:48:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] Zbog uspoređivanja,

1094
00:48:17,559 --> 00:48:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] zato što nisam radila na osobnom odnosu s Bogom,

1095
00:48:21,460 --> 00:48:23,780
[SPEAKER_00] zbog nerešavanja problema.

1096
00:48:23,780 --> 00:48:26,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ipak Otac dalje

1097
00:48:26,280 --> 00:48:27,699
[SPEAKER_00] blagosljivlja i daje.

1098
00:48:27,699 --> 00:48:28,719
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto?

1099
00:48:29,760 --> 00:48:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što on nikad

1100
00:48:31,099 --> 00:48:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] ne napušta ono što je započeo u nekome.

1101
00:48:34,880 --> 00:48:37,199
[SPEAKER_00] I nikad neće ostaviti

1102
00:48:37,199 --> 00:48:39,760
[SPEAKER_00] nedovršeno svoje dijelo u drugome.

1103
00:48:39,760 --> 00:48:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nikad neće ostaviti nedovršen

1104
00:48:43,500 --> 00:48:44,780
[SPEAKER_00] plan

1105
00:48:44,780 --> 00:48:47,320
[SPEAKER_00] za život svoje djece.

1106
00:48:48,139 --> 00:48:50,360
[SPEAKER_00] I sve ono što je nesavršeno

1107
00:48:50,360 --> 00:48:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] on može samo usavršiti.

1108
00:48:52,599 --> 00:48:55,900
[SPEAKER_00] I zato neka mu je hvala i slava.

1109
00:48:55,900 --> 00:48:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

